When you turn on the air purifier remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle is in the parking gear and six doors (main drive door, passenger door, left rear door, right rear door, trunk, hood) are all closed.

"1. Turn on the defroster
When you turn on the defroster remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle is in the parking gear, the main drive door is locked and six doors (main drive door, passenger door, left rear door, right rear door, trunk, hood) are all closed.
2. Turn off the defroster
When you turn off the defroster remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle speed is 0 and and the main drive door is locked. The engine must be started locally and the engine cannot be turned off when the defroster is being turned off."

"1. Turn on the engine
Turn on the engine remotely, you need to make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle is in the parking gear, the power and engine are off, the main driving door is locked and six doors (main drive door, passenger door, left rear door, right rear door, trunk, hood) are all closed.
2. Turn off the engine
When you remotely turn off the engine, you need to make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle speed is 0 and the main vehicle door lock is closed. Only the motor turned on remotely can be turned off remotely."

When you turn on the cockpit cleaning remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the battery is fully charged, the vehicle is in the parking gear and six doors (main drive door, passenger door, left rear door, right rear door, trunk, hood) are all closed; this function is external air circulation. It is recommended not to turn it on under harsh external conditions.

"1. Turn on the seat heating
When you turn on the seat heating remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle is in the parking gear, the main drive door is locked and six doors (main drive door, passenger door, left rear door, right rear door, trunk, hood) are all closed.
2. Turn off the seat heating
When you turn off the seat heating remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle speed is 0 and and the main drive door is locked. The engine must be started locally and the engine cannot be turned off if the seat heating is being turned off."

"1. Turn on the seat ventilation
When you turn on the seat ventilation remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle is in the parking gear, the main drive door is locked and six doors (main drive door, passenger door, left rear door, right rear door, trunk, hood) are all closed.
2. Turn off the seat ventilation
When you turn off the seat ventilation remotely, please make sure the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle speed is 0 and and the main drive door is locked. The engine must be started locally and the engine cannot be turned off when the seat ventilation is being turned off."
When you controll the sunroof remotely, it must be ensured the vehicle network signal is good, the vehicle is in the parking gear.

"Notice
1. The departure time must be 15 minutes later than the current time. The departure time is the end time of the battery pack heating execution. 2. When the departure time is >15min from the current time, ≤1h: the vehicle will immediately perform battery pack heating. 3. If the departure time is >1h from the current time: the vehicle will start heating the heating pack when it is 1h away from the departure time. 4. When the departure time is earlier than the current time, the battery pack heating will be performed at the corresponding time of the next day. 5. After the setting is completed, it will only be executed once, and will not be executed repeatedly."
